    "content": "<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Agile Methodology | Visual Journey</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary: #6366f1;\n            --primary-light: #818cf8;\n            --secondary: #10b981;\n            --accent: #f59e0b;\n            --dark: #1e293b;\n            --light: #f8fafc;\n            --transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);\n        }\n\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            background-color: var(--light);\n            color: var(--dark);\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 3rem;\n            opacity: 0;\n            transform: translateY(20px);\n            animation: fadeIn 1s 0.3s forwards;\n        }\n\n        h1 {\n            font-size: 3.5rem;\n            font-weight: 800;\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), var(--secondary));\n            -webkit-background-clip: text;\n            background-clip: text;\n            color: transparent;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            line-height: 1.2;\n        }\n\n        .subtitle {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            color: #64748b;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            height: 80vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .agile-wheel {\n            width: 600px;\n            height: 600px;\n            position: relative;\n            margin: 3rem auto;\n            opacity: 0;\n            transform: scale(0.8);\n            animation: scaleIn 1s 0.6s forwards;\n        }\n\n        .wheel-center {\n            position: absolute;\n            width: 120px;\n            height: 120px;\n            background: var(--primary);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            top: 50%;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            color: white;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);\n            z-index: 10;\n        }\n\n        .wheel-spoke {\n            position: absolute;\n            width: 250px;\n            height: 4px;\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), var(--primary-light));\n            top: 50%;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform-origin: left center;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            opacity: 0;\n        }\n\n        .spoke-1 { transform: translate(0, -50%) rotate(0deg); animation: spokeIn 0.8s 1s forwards; }\n        .spoke-2 { transform: translate(0, -50%) rotate(60deg); animation: spokeIn 0.8s 1.2s forwards; }\n        .spoke-3 { transform: translate(0, -50%) rotate(120deg); animation: spokeIn 0.8s 1.4s forwards; }\n        .spoke-4 { transform: translate(0, -50%) rotate(180deg); animation: spokeIn 0.8s 1.6s forwards; }\n        .spoke-5 { transform: translate(0, -50%) rotate(240deg); animation: spokeIn 0.8s 1.8s forwards; }\n        .spoke-6 { transform: translate(0, -50%) rotate(300deg); animation: spokeIn 0.8s 2s forwards; }\n\n        .wheel-node {\n            position: absolute;\n            width: 80px;\n            height: 80px;\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--dark);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n            transform: scale(0);\n            transition: var(--transition);\n        }\n\n        .node-1 { top: 50%; left: calc(50% + 250px); transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0); animation: nodeIn 0.6s 1.3s forwards; }\n        .node-2 { top: calc(50% - 216.5px); left: calc(50% + 125px); transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0); animation: nodeIn 0.6s 1.5s forwards; }\n        .node-3 { top: calc(50% - 216.5px); left: calc(50% - 125px); transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0); animation: nodeIn 0.6s 1.7s forwards; }\n        .node-4 { top: 50%; left: calc(50% - 250px); transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0); animation: nodeIn 0.6s 1.9s forwards; }\n        .node-5 { top: calc(50% + 216.5px); left: calc(50% - 125px); transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0); animation: nodeIn 0.6s 2.1s forwards; }\n        .node-6 { top: calc(50% + 216.5px); left: calc(50% + 125px); transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0); animation: nodeIn 0.6s 2.3s forwards; }\n\n        .wheel-node:hover {\n            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.1) !important;\n            box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);\n        }\n\n        .node-icon {\n            width: 40px;\n            height: 40px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            color: white;\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .node-1 .node-icon { background-color: var(--primary); }\n        .node-2 .node-icon { background-color: var(--secondary); }\n        .node-3 .node-icon { background-color: var(--accent); }\n        .node-4 .node-icon { background-color: #ef4444; }\n        .node-5 .node-icon { background-color: #8b5cf6; }\n        .node-6 .node-icon { background-color: #3b82f6; }\n\n        .node-content {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            opacity: 0;\n            transform: translateY(10px);\n            transition: var(--transition);\n        }\n\n        .wheel-node:hover .node-content {\n            opacity: 1;\n            transform: translateY(0);\n        }\n\n        .sprints-container {\n            margin-top: 5rem;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            gap: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .sprint {\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 1rem;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 2rem;\n            opacity: 0;\n            transform: translateY(20px);\n        }\n\n        .sprint:nth-child(1) { animation: fadeInUp 0.8s 2.5s forwards; }\n        .sprint:nth-child(2) { animation: fadeInUp 0.8s 2.7s forwards; }\n        .sprint:nth-child(3) { animation: fadeInUp 0.8s 2.9s forwards; }\n\n        .sprint-phase {\n            width: 80px;\n            height: 80px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-light));\n            border-radius: 1rem;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            color: white;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            flex-shrink: 0;\n        }\n\n        .sprint-content h3 {\n            color: var(--primary);\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .sprint-content p {\n            color: #64748b;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .controls {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 1rem;\n            margin-top: 3rem;\n            opacity: 0;\n            animation: fadeIn 0.8s 3.2s forwards;\n        }\n\n        .btn {\n            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;\n            border-radius: 0.5rem;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: var(--transition);\n            border: none;\n        }\n\n        .btn-primary {\n            background: var(--primary);\n            color: white;\n        }\n\n        .btn-primary:hover {\n            background: var(--primary-light);\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .btn-outline {\n            background: transparent;\n            color: var(--primary);\n            border: 2px solid var(--primary);\n        }\n\n        .btn-outline:hover {\n            background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 5rem;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            color: #64748b;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            opacity: 0;\n            animation: fadeIn 0.8s 3.5s forwards;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes fadeIn {\n            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes scaleIn {\n            to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes spokeIn {\n            to { opacity: 0.3; }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes nodeIn {\n            to { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes fadeInUp {\n            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .agile-wheel {\n                width: 300px;\n                height: 300px;\n            }\n\n            .wheel-node {\n                width: 60px;\n                height: 60px;\n                font-size: 0.8rem;\n            }\n\n            .node-1 { left: calc(50% + 125px); }\n            .node-2 { top: calc(50% - 108.25px); left: calc(50% + 62.5px); }\n            .node-3 { top: calc(50% - 108.25px); left: calc(50% - 62.5px); }\n            .node-4 { left: calc(50% - 125px); }\n            .node-5 { top: calc(50% + 108.25px); left: calc(50% - 62.5px); }\n            .node-6 { top: calc(50% + 108.25px); left: calc(50% + 62.5px); }\n\n            .wheel-spoke {\n                width: 125px;\n            }\n\n            h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5rem;\n            }\n\n            .sprint {\n                flex-direction: column;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <header>\n            <h1>Agile Methodology</h1>\n            <p class=\"subtitle\">A visual journey through the principles and practices that revolutionize modern software development</p>\n        </header>\n\n        <div class=\"hero\">\n            <div class=\"agile-wheel\">\n                <div class=\"wheel-center\">Agile</div>\n                <div class=\"wheel-spoke spoke-1\"></div>\n                <div class=\"wheel-spoke spoke-2\"></div>\n                <div class=\"wheel-spoke spoke-3\"></div>\n                <div class=\"wheel-spoke spoke-4\"></div>\n                <div class=\"wheel-spoke spoke-5\"></div>\n                <div class=\"wheel-spoke spoke-6\"></div>\n                \n                <div class=\"wheel-node node-1\">\n                    <div class=\"node-icon\">1</div>\n                    <div class=\"node-content\">\n                        Customer Collaboration\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"wheel-node node-2\">\n                    <div class=\"node-icon\">2</div>\n                    <div class=\"node-content\">\n                        Iterative Development\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"wheel-node node-3\">\n                    <div class=\"node-icon\">3</div>\n                    <div class=\"node-content\">\n                        Adaptive Planning\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"wheel-node node-4\">\n                    <div class=\"node-icon\">4</div>\n                    <div class=\"node-content\">\n                        Continuous Improvement\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"wheel-node node-5\">\n                    <div class=\"node-icon\">5</div>\n                    <div class=\"node-content\">\n                        Cross-functional Teams\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"wheel-node node-6\">\n                    <div class=\"node-icon\">6</div>\n                    <div class=\"node-content\">\n                        Delivering Value\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"sprints-container\">\n            <div class=\"sprint\">\n                <div class=\"sprint-phase\">S1</div>\n                <div class=\"sprint-content\">\n                    <h3>Planning</h3>\n                    <p>The team defines the sprint goal and selects product backlog items to work on during the sprint. Tasks are broken down and estimated.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"sprint\">\n                <div class=\"sprint-phase\">S2</div>\n                <div class=\"sprint-content\">\n                    <h3>Development</h3>\n                    <p>Team members work on their tasks, collaborating daily. The product increment is developed with continuous integration and testing.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"sprint\">\n                <div class=\"sprint-phase\">S3</div>\n                <div class=\"sprint-content\">\n                    <h3>Review & Retrospective</h3>\n                    <p>The sprint concludes with a review of the completed work and a retrospective to discuss improvements for the next sprint.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"controls\">\n            <button class=\"btn btn-primary\" id=\"animateBtn\">Replay Animation</button>\n            <button class=\"btn btn-outline\" id=\"learnBtn\">Learn More</button>\n        </div>\n\n        <footer>\n            <p>© 2023 Agile Methodology Visualization | Designed for aesthetic excellence</p>\n        </footer>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n            const animateBtn = document.getElementById('animateBtn');\n            const learnBtn = document.getElementById('learnBtn');\n            \n            animateBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {\n                // Reload the page to replay animations\n                window.location.reload();\n            });\n            \n            learnBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {\n                alert('For more detailed information about Agile Methodology, visit agilealliance.org or scrum.org');\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>"
